>\necho -n &quot;<em>YOURBOTKEYHERE</em>&quot; &gt; Bot_token.txt"},{"pid":"6cdc3fe64b8e83230da84f13f99eb2b1d39172f1","tid":433064,"uid":54571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>馬料水巴打 整好左個.py file點掛上去raspberry pi, 就咁好似run唔到 :(</blockquote><br />\n1. 裝返曬Dependencies e.g. python-telegram-bot, python3, python3-pip<br />\n2. 係Raspberry Pi度開個shell打python3 <em>YOUR_PROGRAM</em>.py<br />\n<br />\n因為Vim, Nano, Gedit天生柒, 會幫你加newline係file尾, 所以要咁樣去set Bot Key<br />\necho -n &quot;<em>YOURBOTKEYHERE</em>&quot; &gt; Bot_token.txt</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=c7940054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba6c2759bd04c8517e10609f076b50d35b2490f","tid":433064,"uid":153427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>馬料水巴打 整好左個.py file點掛上去raspberry pi, 就咁好似run唔到 :(</blockquote><br />\n1. 裝返曬Dependencies e.g. python-telegram-bot, python3, python3-pip<br />\n2. 係Raspberry Pi度開個shell打python3 <em>YOUR_PROGRAM</em>.py<br />\n<br />\n因為Vim, Nano, Gedit天生柒, 會幫你加newline係file尾, 所以要咁樣去set Bot Key<br />\necho -n &quot;<em>YOURBOTKEYHERE</em>&quot; &gt; Bot_token.txt</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=c7940054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係Terminal打<br />\n<em>sudo pip3 install python-telegram-bot</em>"},{"pid":"3af12f6409abc4f4f03c08d32c62da901909bbc2","tid":433064,"uid":54571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>馬料水巴打 整好左個.py file點掛上去raspberry pi, 就咁好似run唔到 :(</blockquote><br />\n1. 裝返曬Dependencies e.g. python-telegram-bot, python3, python3-pip<br />\n2. 係Raspberry Pi度開個shell打python3 <em>YOUR_PROGRAM</em>.py<br />\n<br />\n因為Vim, Nano, Gedit天生柒, 會幫你加newline係file尾, 所以要咁樣去set Bot Key<br />\necho -n &quot;<em>YOURBOTKEYHERE</em>&quot; &gt; Bot_token.txt</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/15/223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F15%2F223937_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=c7940054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係Terminal打<br />\n<em>sudo pip3 install python-telegram-bot</em></blockquote><br />\n得左, thanks!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8120fe2f79ded8a7619e46f51168fa3e4b57ce","tid":433064,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"311fad14ff86ed8c46aa3aea022f5619371c5454","tid":433064,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩試左 係work 既 但係一唔用佢一陣就timeout 係咩原因？"},{"pid":"f34ba0453ca8f21a70d65b74a3f24c0d0104990d","tid":433064,"uid":117978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"open source?"},{"pid":"44fc560c2e370e724cac2bc31dd6f5d8d75d1aae","tid":433064,"uid":153427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩試左 係work 既 但係一唔用佢一陣就timeout 係咩原因？</blockquote><br />\nTelegram唔知自幾時開始就多左timeoutError呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以試下<br />\n<em>Updates = Bot.getUpdates(offset=lastMessageId, timeout=1);</em><br />\n重有try/except呢D進階既concept野, 因為係新手教學所以就無加到"},{"pid":"c6cbe10619ee8e916e34198c54711f7c6a0c6d53","tid":433064,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3e7516491aa579b1e47d5e9a4298de43f035fba3","tid":433064,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩試左 係work 既 但係一唔用佢一陣就timeout 係咩原因？</blockquote><br />\nTelegram唔知自幾時開始就多左timeoutError呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以試下<br />\n<em>Updates = Bot.getUpdates(offset=lastMessageId, timeout=1);</em><br />\n重有try/except呢D進階既concept野, 因為係新手教學所以就無加到</blockquote><br />\n好既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 研究下先"},{"pid":"fdcd6e5a86f7c1184fd81e1b760fd865d552f6d9","tid":433064,"uid":54571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:57:45.000Z","msg":"有冇d香港天氣/其他api json開心share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9629f5f462160fafb5c91306d07280fe70710179","tid":433064,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"想問下如果個bot 想長掛 但係唔想係自己部腦掛 有咩方法 可唔可以放上d server 度掛？"},{"pid":"c5ed8d23957f3be308dd22e479f482a0671cc78b","tid":433064,"uid":54571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下如果個bot 想長掛 但係唔想係自己部腦掛 有咩方法 可唔可以放上d server 度掛？</blockquote><br />\n我用raspberry pi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593ae5745082519797f948df4e02239c74b26f72","tid":433064,"ui